set tw=500
set ai "Auto indent
set si "Smart indent
set wrap "Wrap lines
set nu

nmap <F10> :NERDTreeToggle<CR>
nmap <F9> :set hls!<BAR>set hls?<CR> " 搜索高亮开关

"设置取消备份 禁止临时文件生成
